    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-09-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-09-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="292"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d292">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Signor <persName type="from">Carignani</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Italian Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Manchester, Mass.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-09-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 15, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am in receipt of the following telegram from the minister of foreign affairs:
                        <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>I learn with profound sorrow of the death of the President, the victim of
                            an assassination which has excited the greatest horror in Italy. I beg
                            that you will immediately convey to the Federal Government and the
                            family of the lamented President these sentiments in the name of the
                            Government of the King and in my own.</p>
                        <p rend="right">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Prinetti.</hi>
                        </p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Carignani</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Chargé d’Affaires of Italy.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
